{"TopicId":220223,"ForumId":201,"TopicTitle":"Clouds movement is staggered / stuttered when flying close to them","CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-25T19:55:33Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-25T19:55:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.1.5 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 11 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Ryzen 5 7600X | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Nvidia RTX 4070 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32 GB DDR5\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen flying a plane close to the clouds, you can see them stuttering - their movement is not smooth. See video!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cvideo class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 controls=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.global.core.embeddedvideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Csource type=\u0022video/mp4\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2024_04/KerbalSpaceProgram22023-10-2522-53-24.mp4.1917ae6cd8ee544978cae54261551a75.mp4\u0022\u003E\u003Ca class=\u0022ipsAttachLink\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/attachment.php?id=1470\u0026amp;key=4b293a3bbed69751b1cd1bd32740b3ab\u0022 data-fileid=\u00221470\u0022 data-fileext=\u0022mp4\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EKerbalSpaceProgram22023-10-2522-53-24.mp4\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/video\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-04-11T15:25:39Z\u0022 title=\u002204/11/2024 03:25  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Apr 11\u0022\u003EApril 11\u003C/time\u003E by The Space Peacock\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LorenDB","CreatedById":225325,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-04T15:47:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve noticed this happening especially while moving the camera.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFWIW I have this bug on an AMD Radeon RX 6700 XT, so it\u0027s not an Nvidia glitch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mushylog","CreatedById":227298,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-04T18:40:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would seem YouTuber Matt Lowne also has that animation bug:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/lla5bsSM24I?start=1427\u0026amp;feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022KSP 2 just got a BIG Upgrade!\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mushylog","CreatedById":227298,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-04T19:36:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is a representation of the bug. First part is a brand new save, second is a 4y game-time old save.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/8vhZhv4NILg?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022Clouds animation stutter bug presentation\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PicoSpace","CreatedById":224964,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-14T13:07:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.1.5 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Win10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD 5800x | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A03070 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E64\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyou can see it in the first few seconds of this video (last jump before the countdown WAS an edit but the rest are due to the game).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nOnce take-off occurs there are additional jumps in the clouds but it\u2019s not as noticeable as your focus is on the rocket.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/aNq5uek-IUA?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022SpaceX Integrated Flight Test 2 | But in Kerbal Space Program 2\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot sure why this happens but i have cloud graphics set to maximum.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnote the computer is not overclocked but I\u2019m looking to do some of that next week to see if I can boost performance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cstyle type=\u0022text/css\u0022\u003E\r\n.ipsImage {\r\nwidth: 900px !important;\r\n}\u003C/style\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-14T19:03:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/224964-picospace/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022224964\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/224964-picospace/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@PicoSpace\u003C/a\u003E, merged your bug report.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}